@Next "RX_GETAWAYSTATE"
@Prev "RX_GETLINECOUNT"
@Toc "ARexx"

GETLASTLINE
===========

Usage
     GETLASTLINE

DESCRIPTION:

Returns the last private message received in the format;.
:nick!~user@host Messagetype Nick :message text.

EXAMPLES:

     options results; "getlastline"; "ECHO" result

RELATED TOPICS: See @{"RX_PARSELINE" Link "RX_PARSELINE"}, @{"RX_GETLINE" Link "RX_GETLINE"}.


@EndNode

